quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  36,13,"Wadrib lahum mathalan as-habaalqaryati ith jaaha almursaloon"
  36,14,"Ith arsalna ilayhimu ithnaynifakaththaboohuma faAAazzazna bithalithinfaqaloo inna ilaykum mursaloon"
  36,15,"Qaloo ma antum illabasharun mithluna wama anzala arrahmanumin shay-in in antum illa takthiboon"
  36,16,"Qaloo rabbuna yaAAlamu innailaykum lamursaloon"
  36,17,"Wama AAalayna illaalbalaghu almubeen"
  36,18,"Qaloo inna tatayyarnabikum la-in lam tantahoo lanarjumannakum walayamassannakum minnaAAathabun aleem"
  36,19,"Qaloo ta-irukum maAAakum a-in thukkirtumbal antum qawmun musrifoon"
  36,20,"Wajaa min aqsa almadeenatirajulun yasAAa qala ya qawmi ittabiAAooalmursaleen"
  36,21,"IttabiAAoo man la yas-alukum ajranwahum muhtadoon"
  36,22,"Wama liya la aAAbudu allatheefataranee wa-ilayhi turjaAAoon"
  36,23,"Aattakhithu min doonihi alihatanin yuridni arrahmanu bidurrin la tughniAAannee shafaAAatuhum shay-an wala yunqithoon"
  36,24,"Innee ithan lafee dalalinmubeen"
  36,25,"Innee amantu birabbikum fasmaAAoon"
  36,26,"Qeela odkhuli aljannata qala yalayta qawmee yaAAlamoon"
  36,27,"Bima ghafara lee rabbee wajaAAalaneemina almukrameen"
